overview: Grout Works was developed in 1994 to provide a solution for the problem of dirty, discolored tile grout. With the help of a chemical engineer we developed the first permanent colored grout sealer on the market. Grout Works grout sealer is only available to licensed division owners Nationwide. Grout Works has simplified the process and perfected the art of grout restoration. If you are tired of dirty, discolored grout lines call a Grout Works division near you today!
